          <fr:mainmatter>
            <fr:p>An <fr:strong>affine scheme</fr:strong> is a <fr:link href="algm-000L.xml" title="Locally ringed space" addr="algm-000L" type="local">locally ringed space</fr:link> of the form <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\operatorname {Spec}(R)]]></fr:tex> for some commutative ring <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[R]]></fr:tex>.</fr:p>
